<center><h1><I>Flash</I>: MRC's Membership Newsletter</h1></center>
<P>
<P>
<a href="/mrc/flash/flash.html"><I>Flash</I> updates you monthly </a>on what the <a href="/mrc/about/">MRC</a> is doing to expose and neutralize the left-wing media. Each month you'll learn the most outrageous examples of the media's lies and distortions - and what we're doing to expose it to millions of Americans across the country.<BR>
 <P>

<I>Flash</I> will update you on everything the MRC does - press releases and press conferences, books, 

newsletters, media appearances on TV, radio, and in print, our web site and <a href="/mrc/cyberalert/">CyberAlerts</a>, our special 

reports and studies, joint-projects with other organizations and corporations, and much more.<BR>
<P>


MRC Chairman <a href="/mrc/about/bozelbio.html">L. Brent Bozell</a> gives a report on the liberal media in each issue. He'll detail each project 

the MRC is working on to fight the liberal media.<BR>
<P>


<I>Flash</I>  tells you how MRC's teams of researchers are documenting the left-wing media's assault on 

conservatives and conservative issues. The work of MRC researchers is more important than ever, and 

Flash will keep you informed of the bias they are finding.<BR>
<P>


By reading <I>Flash</I> each month, you'll be assured conservatives are not just letting the media go 

unchecked. <BR>
<P>


Join us, become a member, and help the MRC expose the lies and distortions against conservatives 

by national news media. <BR>
<P>


<a href="/mrc/membership/membership.html.cgi"> Become a Member</a> today and your first issue of <I>Flash</I> will arrive in the next few weeks.  Click <a href="/mrc/flash/flash.html">here</a> to check out back issues.

