<DOCHDR>
http://www.savers.org:80/mrc/reality/realchek.html 204.71.237.73 19970108020506 text/html 3677
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 02:05:19 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 31-Oct-96 16:09:46 GMT
