<hr width=50%>
<!------------------------------------------------------------------->
<I>Wednesday, January 8, 1996</I></CENTER><P>
<P>
Which of the following words can be defined as 
<I>Imitative?</I>
<P>
<P>
<P>
<A HREF="a.html">A. Homiletic</a>
<P>
<A HREF="b.html">B. Fissiparous</a>
<P>
<A HREF="c.html">C. Mimetic</a>
<!------------------------------------------------------------------->
<P>
<P>
<P>
