<li><a href="#Senator Sam Nunn">Senator Sam Nunn</a><br>     
<li><a href="#Pete V. Domenici">Senator Pete V. Domenici<br>     
<li><a href="#Richard K. Armey">Congressman Richard K. Armey</a>  <a href="#Richard K. Armey">etc...</a>, House Majority Leader<br>      
<li><a href="#Connie Mack">Senator Connie Mack</a>,  Chairman, Joint Economic Committee  
</ul>
<p>
<p>
<hr>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<center>
<h4><a name="COMMISSION MEMBERS IN ATTENDANCE">COMMISSION MEMBERS IN ATTENDANCE:</a></h4></center>
<p> 
<p> 
<dd><b>JACK KEMP:</b> Co-Director Empower America</dd> 
<p>
<dd><b>J. KENNETH BLACKWELL:</dd></b> Ohio State Treasurer
